c file to update: `app/platforms/ai-academy/page.tsx`. I will continue to avoid making changes to the landing page files, as per the explicit instructions. I'm moving on to consider the next page, `/platforms/university-oneverse`.\n\n\n**Defining UI Requirements**\n\nI'm now focusing on the University OneVerse Mesh page, outlining its key features. It's an institutional AI operating platform with a visual architectural layout depicting a 4-pillared academic network. Interactive quadrants or tabs will preview operation modes. I'm prioritizing dynamic selectors and tab components representing academic workflows, complete with \"Agent Protocol Logs\" for a simulation effect. Mobile layout will be stacking and scrolling appropriately.\n\n\n**Analyzing Assessment Structure**\n\nI'm now outlining the requirements for the Assessment Mesh page, specifically focusing on the diagnostic validation narrative and visual metaphor of a scanning grid with radial sensors. This will map out key metrics. I will design the interactive assessment simulator representing a dynamic assessment mesh scorecard. I've now identified `app/platforms/assessment-mesh/page.tsx` as the target file.\n\n\n"}}
