ciency] Delegating 42% repetitive workflows to agents...\\n[Status] Simulated ROI: 4.2x compute cost optimization. Roadmap mapped.\"\n  }\n];\n\nexport default function AiAcademyPage() {\n  return (\n    <div className=\"text-white\">Placeholder</div>\n  );\n}\n"}}}
